text: for the salmon on route remember roll
out the pastry evenly put softened
butter into a bowl pick in dill and
roughly chopped basil add zest of one
lemon seasoned and mix pat dry salmon
Phillips and seasoned spread herb butter
on one side and whole-grain mustard on
the other sandwich the Phillips place
the salmon in the center of the pastry
and brush around it with egg wash season
to make the parcel trim away excess
pastry fold turn upside down and place
on a non-stick baking tray brush with
egg white crosshatch and score portions
